{"title":"春之歌","authors":["赵灼臣"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":3,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春之歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈尔滨铁路局敖头站扳道员　赵灼臣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车轮隆隆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笛声欢叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碾碎坚实的积雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驶过明亮的轨道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鱼贯似的车辆啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满载着钢管、水泥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤炭、铁板、木料，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带来了春天的报告。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工厂板报群前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一伙年青人忙得汗流满面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产捷报刚写上标题，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的创造又飞出了车间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢水托着朝阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂起晨曦万丈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利的歌声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汇成了欢乐的海洋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在机床前，在高炉旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在矿井下，在田野上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少颗火热的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在精心绘制着春的图样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的战斗行列，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越来越壮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们亲爱的祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无比坚强！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的中国共产党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引导我们从胜利走向胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想的光辉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照彻了远山重洋！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们迈开雄壮的步伐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一齐走向斗争前线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要用勤劳的双手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为祖国绘制一个永恒的春天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自《前进列车》〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}